{"tid":2001124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續休息啦香港人...","createTime":"2020-05-04T10:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T11:20:53.000Z","uid":288018,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8287f2a44f7fe5af4a8457df5d51cf8176bfc3e3","tid":2001124,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:11:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n打機既打機<br />\n訓教既訓教.</span></strong></span><br />\n繼續做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93LjjPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93LjjPc.jpg&h=876cc897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家係咪已經剩係記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">抗疫</span></strong>，唔記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭</span></span></strong><br />\n三十幾度天氣情況下戴住口罩既小妹妹黎問我，可唔可以擺底文宣係鋪頭...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到個下。心都UP埋<br />\n唔洗返工既香港人 ，你地做緊咩？<br />\n一班後生仔一直都提醒緊我地<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭從沒停止過</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人</span></span></strong>最叻係<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">善忘</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">習慣</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪唔記得左我地失去左有幾多手足？<br />\n有幾多<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>被自殺</strong></span>？<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">被失蹤</span></strong>？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OF5rKiO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOF5rKiO.jpg&h=13180866&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCPLZSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCPLZSa.jpg&h=efd0f67e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mHarxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mHarxb.jpg&h=95ddae54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbJ1ycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbJ1ycc.jpg&h=99a097b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/obMbaYT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FobMbaYT.jpg&h=76941caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>夠鐘</strong></span></span>醒啦⋯⋯<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好令已失去既手足白白咁犧牲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n五大訴求。缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 🇭🇰。時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ff862047245dbae638f5920a7ec4c2c26b69db","tid":2001124,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"35 + thx lor"},{"pid":"8ebe28672099c4e9ba042d925c93334ca361f438","tid":2001124,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"推醒你地"},{"pid":"4149de28d22c91cffc1a58cbf4d938aa6edb30ba","tid":2001124,"uid":327932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7156dde4523946d1ab0fcae49d13b1636273626b","tid":2001124,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"推醒你地"},{"pid":"af04351a13